Nigerian artiste who has been struggling to find his feat in the music industry, ever since his spat with the Okoyes, Mr. May D has signed under DMW music group. Mr. May D discontinued his own record label “Confam” to join Davido’s DMW label in a means to revive back his extinct career.  He took to his official twitter page to confirm this by putting up DMW and 30BG logo with a confirmation caption as a clear doubt after featuring Davido in a yet to released song “Lowo Lowo”.